985.name: AA 2209-P
985.Applications: Duplex stainless steels in chemical industry such as offshore, tubing, vessel, boilers etc..
985.Suitable_For: Welding wrought, forged or cast duplex stainless steels in the as welded condition. Also suitable for dissimilar welding of low alloyed steels and common stainless steels, UNS S31803, S32205, UR 45N & UR 45N+, 2205, SAF 2205 Fafer 4462, NKCr22, SM22Cr, Falc 223 UNS S32304 : UR 35 N SAF 2304W.Nr: 1.4462, X2CrNiMoN 22 5 3, 1.4362, X2CrNiN 23 4,  1.4463, 1.4460, 1.4583
